snippet.textDisplay: I like Coke Studio Pakistan all over but I give thumbs to very few which I like to listen at special times. This is one of them. This is the best so far in coke studio 10.... majorly because the lyrics are specifically handcrafted for this song, music is very soothing and sublime. But the most important aspect.... kya kahoon yaaron, is nazm ki surkhiyon ne hamein hamara ateet yaad krva liya.... completely lost in reminiscence of my beautiful ex and discussions which we had cross-border😢
